      "raw_text": "know which was which. The coun.\ncilmen apparently didn't dare say,\nbut as in all such cases referred\nthe communication to the commit\ntee of the whole, where it may re-\nmain until the public forces the\ncouncil to take action. The Wash\nington Water Power company\nseems to be bringing pressure to\nbear upon the councilmen. Not\nthat an additional expense of 5000\nwill be more than a drop in the\nbucket, but because the company\ndoes not want to be held up to the\npublic as being governed by the\nlegislative body Of the city. The\ncompany is in the habit of getting\neverything for nothing and hates to\nbreak it, apparently."
